net.sf.jclec.mo

Interface IMOAlgorithm

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MOECAlgorithm, MOEPAlgorithm, MOESAlgorithm, MOGeneticAlgorithm, MOGPAlgorithm, MOOnlyRecombinatorAlgorithm, MOPSOAlgorithm

    public interface IMOAlgorithm
    This interface specifies the required methods that any multi-objective algorithm should implement.

    HISTORY:

    • (AR|JRR|SV, 1.0, March 2018) First release.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Aurora Ramirez (AR), Jose Raul Romero (JRR), Sebastian Ventura (SV)

    Knowledge Discovery and Intelligent Systems (KDIS) Research Group: http://www.uco.es/grupos/kdis
